TC-041: NEGATIVE - Verify Direct Slug Navigation
Objective: Validate known issue with slug-based URLs
Priority: High
Type: Negative

Test Steps:
Attempt to access https://tmdb-discover.surge.sh/popular
Observe behavior (page load, errors, redirects)
Check browser console for errors
Verify if content loads correctly
Attempt refresh on the slug URL

Expected Result (Bug):
Direct slug access may fail
404 or blank page displayed
Console shows routing errors
This is a known defect - document actual behavior

Test Data: /popular, /trending, /newest, /top-rated
